template.description: Ingest Stratux data from WS and output to Phoenix, Kafka, InfluxDB
template.name: Stratux Traffic to Various Endpoints

entry.value: upsert into stratux.traffic values ('${'row_key'}',${'addr_type'},${'age'},${'age_last_alt'},${'alt'},'${'alt_is_gnss'}',${'bearing'},'${'bearing_dist_valid'}',${'distance'},${'emitter_category'},'${'extrapolated_pos'}',${'gnss_diff_from_baro_alt'},${'icao_addr'},'${'last_alt'}','${'last_gnss_diff'}',${'last_gnss_diff_alt'},'${'last_seen'}',${'last_source'},'${'last_speed'}',cast(${'lat'} as float),cast(${'lng'} as float),${'nacp'},${'nic'},'${'on_ground'}','${'pos_valid'}',${'priority_status'},'${'reg'}',${'signal_level'},${'speed'},'${'speed_valid'}',${'squawk'},'${'tail'}',${'target_type'},'${'time_stamp'}',${'track'},${'vvel'})

processors.name: Capture S Code and TS for Key
